window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>He’s the alpha of the pack. She’s a witch on the run. Until one stormy night changes everything.</i></b><br> <br> Colt Savage is the alpha of the Copper Canyon wolf pack, dedicating his life to protecting his pack and running the family ranch with unwavering commitment.<br> <br> One stormy night, a mysterious and battered young woman named Briar arrives at the ranch. The moment Colt catches her scent—an intoxicating aroma that stirs his very soul—he knows she's different. His wolf recognizes her as his fated mate.<br> <br> As Briar settles into ranch life, the chemistry between them becomes undeniable. Yet, she guards her secrets closely. When Colt finally confronts her, Briar reveals a shocking truth: she is a powerful witch on the run from a coven that seeks to exploit her immense abilities.<br> <br> Colt vows to protect her, but trust doesn't come easy within the pack. With tensions rising, he finds himself caught between pack politics and the relentless attacks from her coven. Loyalties are tested, and dangers lurk around every corner.<br> <br> Can Briar harness her powers to vanquish the threats once and for all? Will the secrets she holds spell doom for the Copper Canyon pack? In a battle where loyalty and love are put to the ultimate test, Colt and Briar must fight not just for their lives, but for a future together.<br> <br> <b>Alpha’s Claim</b> is the thrilling first book in the <i>Copper Canyon Shifters</i> series. Dive into a world where passion meets magic in a gripping tale of love, loyalty, and supernatural suspense.</p>"; 
